  <name>LMarbles</name>
  <summary>Atomix clone with a slight change in concept</summary>
  <description>
    <p>LMarbles is an Atomix clone with a slight change in concept. Instead of assembling molecules
      you create figures out of marbles.</p>
    <p>Nevertheless, the basic game play is the same:
      If a marble starts to move it will not stop until it hits a wall or another marble.
      To make it more interesting there are obstacles like one-way streets, crumbling walls and portals.
      You can either play against a move or a time limit.</p>
  </description>
